<% data = adapter.panel_data %>
<% if data[:error] %>
## Pool state

_Could not read pool state: <%= data[:error] %>_
<% else %>
## Pool state (<%= adapter.protocol_name %>)

- **Pair:** <%= data[:token0][:symbol] %> / <%= data[:token1][:symbol] %>
- **Fee tier:** <%= data[:fee_pct] %>
<% if data[:price_0_per_1] %>
- **Price:** 1 <%= data[:token1][:symbol] %> ≈ <%= number_with_delimiter(data[:price_0_per_1].round(6)) %> <%= data[:token0][:symbol] %>
- **Inverse price:** 1 <%= data[:token0][:symbol] %> = <%= data[:price_1_per_0] %> <%= data[:token1][:symbol] %>
<% end %>
- **Current tick:** <%= number_with_delimiter(data[:tick]) %>
- **Active liquidity:** <%= number_with_delimiter(data[:liquidity]) %>
<% if data[:tvl_usd] %>
- **TVL:** $<%= number_with_delimiter(data[:tvl_usd].round(0)) %> (via DefiLlama)
<% end %>

### Tokens

- **token0** — <%= data[:token0][:symbol] %> (`<%= data[:token0][:address] %>`), <%= data[:token0][:decimals] %> decimals
- **token1** — <%= data[:token1][:symbol] %> (`<%= data[:token1][:address] %>`), <%= data[:token1][:decimals] %> decimals
<% end %>
